file.name: components.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.2
info:
  version: 0.0.1
  title: '@viron/example-golang components'

components:
  parameters:
    IdPathParam:
      name: id
      in: path
      schema:
        type: string
      required: true

    PagerSizeQueryParam:
      name: size
      in: query
      description: Size of list
      schema:
        type: integer
      required: false
    PagerPageQueryParam:
      name: page
      in: query
      description: Page number of list
      schema:
        type: integer
      required: false
    SortQueryParam:
      name: sort
      in: query
      description: Sort specification of list
      schema:
        type: array
        minItems: 1
        items:
          type: string
          pattern: "^.+?:(asc|desc)$"
      style: form
      explode: false

    IdQueryParam:
      name: id
      in: query
      schema:
        type: string
      required: false

  schemas:
    Pager:
      type: object
      properties:
        maxPage:
          type: integer
        currentPage:
          type: integer
      required:
        - maxPage
        - currentPage

    CreatedAt:
      description: 作成日時
      type: string
      format: date-time

    UpdatedAt:
      description: 更新日時
      type: string
      format: date-time

  securitySchemes:
    jwt:
      type: oauth2
      flows:
        implicit:
          authorizationUrl: https://localhost:3000/signin
          scopes:
            api:access: API access
